            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "hi, you can try this:\n\n```\ncommand! -nargs=* -complete=customlist,TestFn TestCmd echo\nfunc TestFn(a, b, c)\n    \" return map(range(1, 50), 'printf(\"%d\", v:val)')\n    \" return map(range(1, 50), 'printf(\"%s%d\", a:a, v:val)')\nendfunc\n```\n\nuncomment one return statement, `:TestCmd --type=` and press `<tab>`\n\n<img width=\"1040\" height=\"301\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c4d4b760-9a8b-44d7-942b-cc13e2ac6e81\" />\n\n<img width=\"1007\" height=\"297\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/40f6ec1a-b2e0-49dd-a06b-bbb242c1ae10\" />",
